data.description:
Motivated! Lovely Home on 12 acres with shop with electricity. In the country, yet close to town, this pretty 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has large family room with wood burning fireplace and vaulted ceilings, breakfast room, formal dining, office with closet which may be used as 4th bedroom, lots of storage and large laundry room.  Kitchen has granite counter tops, island with second sink, breakfast bar, double ovens and pantry. Large patio provides plenty of room for entertaining and enjoying the country. There are 2 septics systems and a large generator. There is an ag exemption in place.


This information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buyer's agent and buyer to verify.
